',1),(282,'2025-01-17 10:20:56.055371','2025-01-17 10:20:56.055371',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,'update','Updated post #3','post',3,'{\"title\": \"MUSIC DRAMA COMPETITION SET TO ROCK THE STAGE!\", \"content\": \"\\nKampala, Uganda - Arena Sports Academy is thrilled to announce the upcoming Music Drama Competition, scheduled to take place on October 10th, 2024.\\n\\nThis highly anticipated event invites dance crews of youth aged 5-25 to showcase their talents and compete for exciting prizes. The competition promises to be an electrifying display of music, dance, and drama, with participants vying for cash prizes, trophies, and performance opportunities.\\n\\n\\\"We are excited to provide a platform for young talent to shine,\\\" said Mr. Nsamba, founder of Arena Sports Academy. \\\"This competition is a celebration of creativity, self-expression, and youth empowerment.\\\"\\n\\nRegistration for the competition is now open, and interested participants can contact Arena Sports Academy Uganda for more information.\\n\\nMark your calendars for October 10th, 2024, and get ready to experience the ultimate music drama extravaganza!\\n\\nEvent Details:\\n\\n- Date: October 10th, 2024\\n- Time: 8am-4pm\\n- Venue: Wankulukuku\\n- Age Group: 5-25 years\\n- Registration: Contact Arena Sports Academy for more information\\n\\nStay tuned for updates!\", \"category\": \"events\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dgjtaqrhg/image/upload/v1736463382/Orange_and_Violet_Competition_Dance_Competition_Poster_x4c6e9.png\", \"videoUrl\": \"\"}','{\"id\": 3, \"title\": \"MUSIC DRAMA COMPETITION SET TO ROCK THE STAGE!\", \"content\": \"\\nKampala, Uganda - Arena Sports Academy is thrilled to announce the upcoming Music Drama Competition, scheduled to take place on October 10th, 2024.\\n\\nThis highly anticipated event invites dance crews of youth aged 5-25 to showcase their talents and compete for exciting prizes. The competition promises to be an electrifying display of music, dance, an